#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Sattāvāsavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 27. Paṭhamaverasutta → paṭhamaverabhayasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Paṭhamaverasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Yato kho, gahapati, ariyasāvakassa pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti, "
"catūhi ca sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, so ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ "
"byākareyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.406"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:3.1"
msgid "Katamāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, gahapati, pāṇātipātī pāṇātipātapaccayā diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ "
"domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, pāṇātipātā paṭivirato neva diṭṭhadhammikampi "
"bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na "
"cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:3.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā paṭiviratassa evaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ vūpasantaṃ hoti. (1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:4.1"
msgid "Yaṃ, gahapati, adinnādāyī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:4.2"
msgid "kāmesumicchācārī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:4.3"
msgid "musāvādī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:4.4"
msgid ""
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānapaccayā "
"diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato neva diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, na samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na cetasikampi dukkhaṃ "
"domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:4.5"
msgid ""
"Surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratassa evaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ vūpasantaṃ "
"hoti. (4–5.)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:5.1"
msgid "Imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:6.1"
msgid "“Katamehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:6.2"
msgid "Idha, gahapati, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:7.1"
msgid "Dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:7.2"
msgid ""
"‘svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī’ti. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.407"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:8.1"
msgid "Saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:8.2"
msgid ""
"‘suppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho ujuppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho "
"ñāyappaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho sāmīcippaṭipanno bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṅgho; yadidaṃ cattāri purisayugāni aṭṭha purisapuggalā esa bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṅgho āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ "
"puññakkhettaṃ lokassā’ti. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:9.1"
msgid ""
"Ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi acchiddehi asabalehi "
"akammāsehi bhujissehi viññuppasatthehi aparāmaṭṭhehi samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:9.2"
msgid "Imehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an9.27:10.1"
msgid ""
"Yato kho, gahapati, ariyasāvakassa imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni "
"honti, imehi ca catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, so ākaṅkhamāno "
"attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.27:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto; sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.27:10.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
